setJoinedStrategy(bytes32,address,bool).details: set value to true if a user joins a strategy, else, false

params._connector: The address of the connector to toggle.

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner. Setting `newOwner` to the zero address is allowed; this can be used to cancel an initiated ownership transfer.

params._amounts: corresponding amounts of each asset being deposited.
params._assets: list of asset addresses associated with the deposits.
params._performanceFee: the performance fee generated by the strategy.
params._strategyId: unique identifier of the strategy to update.

params._indicator: determines the operation:                   0 to add a strategyId,                   any other value to remove the strategyId.
params._strategyId: unique identifier of the strategy to update.
params._user: address of the user whose strategy is being updated.

params._amount: the amount of token to add or sub.
params._indicator: determines the operation:                   0 to add,                   any other value to sub.
params._user: address of the user whose balance is being updated.
